         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1 #a2"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:krauseandthomas1964"/><citedRange>68</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>25</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2 #a3"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:carling2000"/><citedRange>71, 116</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2 #a3 #a4 #a5"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>25, 132</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3 #a4"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1954"/><citedRange>761</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>58</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1983"/><citedRange>30</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4 #a5"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:carling2000"/><citedRange>50, 117</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>472 n.1</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1954"/><citedRange>753</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1969"/><citedRange>236</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">Und um den pāṃsukūlika-Mönch [bzw. die pāṃsukūlika-Mönche] zu trösten, kam der Buddha, der Lehrer, zusammen mit Ananda zur Leichenstätte.</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">And in order to comfort the pāṃsukūlika-monk [or the pāṃsukūlika-monks], the Buddha, the teacher, came with Ananda to the charnel-ground.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>472, fn. 1</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a5"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">Mit [seiner] lotusfarbenen, zarten Hand nahm er [scil. der Buddha] das über die gestorbene Frau gedeckte Tuch [fort].</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">With [his] lotus-coloured, tender had, he [i.e. the Buddha] took [away] the cloth [that had been] spread over the woman [who had] died.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>400</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
